      "rationale": "Pedicle screw construct operates in predominantly elastic regime under F1717 loading up to yield. Linear elastic material model with frictional contact (mu=0.2) at screw-vertebral body interface. Sensitivity study confirms contact friction coefficient has <3% influence on stiffness QoI. Model form appropriate for intended prediction domain."
